# Project context

At the start of each session, read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root for:

- Build commands, architecture, and code conventions
- Domain model (appointments, auth, permissions)
- **Post-Session Reflection Protocol** (section 8) — run at natural session end

Do not duplicate `AGENTS.md` in other files. Keep `AGENTS.md` as the single source of truth for cross-tool agent guidance (Cursor, Codex, Copilot, etc.).